name: Jellybean king slush
description: We go through the dimensions to crush and serve Jellybean king slush, tyrannically fresh! King Jellybean (also referred to as Mr. Jellybean) was a character featured in the episode "Meeseeks and Destroy". King Jellybean was a giant anthropomorphic jelly bean. It was later revealed that he was the king of a poor village that Rick and Morty agreed to help.
